475
00:33:16,428 --> 00:33:18,205
<i>♪ Before I sleep ♪</i>

476
00:33:18,305 --> 00:33:20,791
<i>♪ The moon shines bright ♪</i>

477
00:33:20,891 --> 00:33:23,168
