00:33:37,449 --> 00:33:39,601
<i>♪ Come a-ti-yi
yippy-yippy-yay, yippy-yay ♪</i>

483
00:33:39,701 --> 00:33:42,020
<i>♪ Come a-ti-yi, yippy-yippy-yay ♪</i>

484
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:44,022
♪♪ (CONTINUES)

