00:33:44,122 --> 00:33:46,024
- Would I?
- No.

486
00:33:46,124 --> 00:33:48,360
COLEY: <i>♪ Give a little yell ♪</i>

487
00:33:48,460 --> 00:33:51,613
♪♪ (WHISTLING)

488
00:33:51,713 --> 00:33:55,117
- ♪♪ (CONTINUES)
- I don't see no point to it.

