715
00:52:15,983 --> 00:52:20,137
Well, just shut up. I can't
take no more of ya. No, sir.

716
00:52:20,237 --> 00:52:22,515
For all the dirty rotten
gall and hate of a thing...

717
00:52:22,615 --> 00:52:25,392
